<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.5.1">
<l>ācai vāycceṉṟa cintaiya rāki</l>
<l rend="indent">yaṉṉai yattaṉeṉ puttirar pūmi</l>
<l>vāca vārkuḻa lāḷeṉṟu mayaṅki</l>
<l rend="indent">māḷu mellaikaṇ vāytiṟa vātē</l>
<l>kēca vāpuru ṭō ttamā veṉṟuṅ</l>
<l rend="indent">kēḻa lākiya kēṭilī yeṉṟum</l>
<l>pēcu vārava reytumpe rumai</l>
<l rend="indent">pēcu vāṉpukil nampara maṉṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those with minds that cling to desire, on the edge of death,</l>
<l rend="indent">[if,] being confused, they do not call out</l>
<l rend="indent">“Mother! Father! My sons! My Land!</l>
<l rend="indent">Lady with fragrance filled locks!”</l>
<l>[but] say “Keśava! Puruṣottama!</l>
<l rend="indent">Imperishable One who became a boar!”</l>
<l>—if speaking of the greatness that they attain,</l>
<l rend="indent">it is not [within] our power.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
